// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mdjBDt rhombic dodecahedron roofs 2023 by jt
// see also https://www.shadertoy.com/view/clfGRn dodecahedron roofs

// Building a rhombic dodecahedron by putting "roofs" (pyramids) on a cube.
// Inspired by a drawing seen in the book Mathematical Snapshots (Kalejdoskop matematyczny) by Hugo Steinhaus.

// This construction helps to understand how to form a rhombic dodecahedral honeycomb
// https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Rhombic_dodecahedral_honeycomb by placing the rhombic dodecahedra on offset grids:
// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/mlfczN rhombic dodecahedra offset grids

// tags: rhombic, dodecahedron, roofs, cube, pyramid

